abstract: >
  SCHISM-ESMF provides Earth System Modeling Framework (ESMF) and 
  NUOPC (National Unified Operational Prediction Capability) caps 
  for the SCHISM (Semi-implicit Cross-scale Hydroscience Integrated 
  System Model) hydrodynamics model. These caps enable SCHISM to be 
  coupled with other Earth system components such as atmospheric 
  models, wave models, sea ice models, and biogeochemical models 
  within standardized coupling frameworks. The package includes both 
  ESMF and NUOPC interfaces, CMake-based build system, example 
  configurations, and comprehensive documentation.

